{"_id":"Spinachandpotatosoup","preptime":"15","servings":"4","keywords":["diet@vegetarian","cook method.hob, oven, grill@hob","cuisine@british traditional","diet@corn-free","diet@yeast-free","diet@egg-free","meal type@soups","diet@peanut-free","diet@wheat-free","special collections@cheffy recommended","special collections@very easy","diet@shellfish-free","main ingredient@vegetables","diet@demi-veg","special collections@budget","diet@gluten-free"],"subtitle":"A wholesome and tasty soup. ","totaltime":"65","cooktime":"50","ingredients":[{"ingredient":"garlic","measure":"1 clove"},{"ingredient":"frozen spinach","measure":"450 g"},{"ingredient":"milk","measure":"450 ml"},{"ingredient":"fromage frais","measure":"150 ml"},{"ingredient":"butter","measure":"25 g"},{"ingredient":"onion","measure":"1"},{"ingredient":"leek","measure":"1"},{"ingredient":"potatoes","measure":"350 g"},{"ingredient":"vegetable stock","measure":"900 ml"},{"ingredient":"lemon juice","measure":"3 tsp"},{"ingredient":"nutmeg","measure":"[sup]1[/sup]/[sub]2[/sub] tsp"},{"ingredient":"seasoning","measure":""}],"method":[{"step":"1","text":"Melt the butter in a large saucepan. Saute onion, leek and potato for 5 min, or until they start to soften and colour."},{"step":"2","text":"Stir in the spinach, lemon juice and garlic and fry for 2-3 min."},{"step":"3","text":"Add stock. Bring to the boil and simmer for 10 min. Allow to cool slightly. Puree the mixture in a blender or food processor until smooth. "},{"step":"4","text":"Return to the pan. Stir in the milk, fromage frais, nutmeg and seasoning. Heat through and serve."}],"title":"Spinach and potato soup"}